    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear you, but it's hard to just \"embrace the stillness\" when the stillness feels like it's swallowing me whole. I just hate feeling so helpless. I hate that I'm just sitting here at the mercy of what my body decides to do next. I wish I felt like I actually had some say in how this all finishes.",
